5 CMD tricks to impress your friends
by Atomic Boy www.youtube.com/user/AtomicBoyGaming

1) Matrix effect
@echo off
color 0a
:top
echo %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random% %random%
goto top

2) Remote shutdown
In CMD: shutdown -i

3) Text files
for /l %%n in (1,1,[number]) do [name] >> [name]%%n.txt

4) CMD title change
in CMD: title [name]

5) CMD color change
CMD > properties > colors

YouTube video: www.youtube.com/watch?v=WUqx8NJMZJg
